Citation.sTitle: Thermodynamic properties of (an ester + and alkane). XVII. Experimental He and Ve values for (an alkyl propanoate + an alkane) at 318.15K
Citation.sAbstract: In this article, we record the experimental values of He and Ve, obtained at a temperature of T=318.15 K and atmospheric pressure for a set of 30 binary mixtures comprised of five alkyl propanoates (methyl to petnyl) with six odd alkanes (heptane to heptadecane).
